END DISPLAY
LINE N 64 96 0 96 
LINE N 320 -224 384 -224 
LINE N 64 -128 0 -128 
LINE N 64 -224 0 -224 
LINE N 320 -96 384 -96 
LINE N 320 -32 384 -32 
